Product description

Functions


Voice Control

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light."

"Hey, Google, turn the light to warm white"

Enjoy hands-free and intelligent life from now on!


16 Million Colors

Cloudy Bay smart recessed light, with more than 16 million colors and 2700K-6500K Cool & Warm White Light provides you the options to change your lights color to fit your changeable scene


Music Sync

Sync to music function meets every kind of your needs. Get ready to have fun with your family and friends!

* Tip: Need to keep the screen on, otherwise the music mode would quit working

Functions


Group Control

Through APP operation, each recessed light can be divided into the living room lighting, bedroom lighting, dining room lighting, they can be controlled as a group or individual. Also, you can share the control LED lights between different devices, having fun setting with family members!


Timer and Schedule

We can use the timer functions for waking up and setting a more ambient mood at bedtime.

It's not just a simple on/ off timer, you can also set a schedule or rhythms, they are waiting for your exploration.


Remote Control

If you forgot to turn off the lights before leaving your home, don’t worry, remote control would help! you can use Cloudy Bay Smart Life App on your tablet or smart phone to control the lights anytime, anywhere. regardless of distance if you have network

Ultra Thin Smart LED Recessed Light with Junction Box

This smart lights are only dimmed by APP and Voice control, not supported by physical dimmer including Triac dimmer, 0-10V dimmer or smart dimmers

If you had to connect to dimmer switch(No normal switch at hand or other suitation), please set the dimmer to most brightness level in case the light flickers and you can only use it as an ON/OFF switch

Dimensions:

LED Panel:3-1/4 " nominent diameter, 1-7/8" illumination diameter ,1" Height,

Junction Box:4" Length,2-3/4" Width,1-3/8" Height

Cut hole size:3"

  • Wattage:9W
  • CRI:90+
  • CCT: 2700K-6500K
  • Lumen: 400lm
  • IC Rated
  • Damp Location
  • Listed: ETL/FCC
